title: Is Soli Bailey Unreasonable?
description: At the ripe old age of 19, Soli Bailey has already established himself as one of the “next” surfers to watch. Hailing from hippie–friendly, laid-back Byron Bay, Soli won the the ASP Australasia Pro Junior Series in 2014 and has his eyes firmly focused on the future.
